:: CustomMacroDemo [docs custom-macro]
!Custom Macro Demo

The macro <<code>><<emojify>><</code>> is defined in <<code>>story.js<</code>> via <<code>>Macro.add()<</code>>.

<<emojify "smile">>
<<emojify "heart">>
<<emojify "star">>
<<emojify "crown">>

!!Passing expression arguments via backticks
<<set _feeling to "happy">>
<<emojify `(_feeling is "happy") ? "smile" : "frown"`>>

<<return "Return to start">>
